{"comments":"Canvas Grid Types — Grid rendering and snap behavior.\n\n## Scope\n\nThis module defines types for canvas grid and snapping:\n\n- **GridStyle**: Visual appearance of grid (dots, lines, isometric, etc.)\n- **GridConfig**: Complete grid configuration\n- **SnapTarget**: What to snap to (grid, objects, guides)\n- **SnapConfig**: Complete snap configuration\n\n## Grid Rendering\n\nGrids support multiple visual styles and can show major/minor divisions.\nGrid visibility is independent of snap behavior.\n\n## Snap Behavior\n\nSnapping provides alignment assistance during object manipulation.\nMultiple snap targets can be active simultaneously.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[83,13],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Canvas/Types/Grid.purs","start":[83,3]},"title":"GridDots"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[84,14],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Canvas/Types/Grid.purs","start":[84,3]},"title":"GridLines"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[85,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Canvas/Types/Grid.purs","start":[85,3]},"title":"GridCrosshairs"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[86,18],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Canvas/Types/Grid.purs","start":[86,3]},"title":"GridIsometric"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[87,20],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Element/Compound/Canvas/Types/Grid.purs","start":[87,3]},"title":"GridPerspective"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Element","Compound"